accommodation.description:
This property was created on a five acre plot that used to be a tobacco growing farmland. Today you will find large shade trees, fruit trees, ornamental shrubs, bamboo groves, whistling pines, and flowering plants that provide a rustic atmosphere to the resort. Well conceived guest rooms are so located to give privacy to our guests. Rooms are well laid out, tastefully furnished, with attached bathrooms providing our guests a comfortable stay.
For our guests who are looking to relax our resort and its immediate surroundings provides a perfect ambiance to take walks, ride bicycles, or do some bird watching. Our guests can unwind in the evenings participating in a tribal dance around a campfire and viewing a documentary film on wildlife.
We are just 200 km from Bangalore, 70 km from Mysore and 95 km from Madikeri (Marcara), well connected by all-weather roads. We are open all year round and the weather is salubrious.
Accommodation;
Jungle Inn has 10 Double Rooms (six regular cozy rooms and four spacious standard rooms), 6 large Swiss Tented Cottages that can accommodate four in each tent and 3family rooms (dormitories) each accommodating six persons. In all 68 persons can be accommodated at a time. All rooms have attached bathrooms with western style water closets and each dormitory has two bathrooms. Swiss Tented Cottages have all the amenities available like other rooms.
Food;
All meals are served at the dining hall. We normally serve traditional Indian food made out of fresh raw materials sourced locally. On occasions we complement with Chinese and Continental dishes. Food is served buffet style, catering both to vegetarians and non-vegetarians. Our food is simple, sumptuous, nutritious and homely food.
Places of interest close to resort;
1. Nagarhole National Park 2. Tibetian monastery (9km from the inn) 3. Tribal setlements (7km from the inn) 4. Lakshman theertha river (5km from the inn) 5. Iruppu falls 6. Tholpetty wildlife park
